{"tid":188440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 點樣可以將傳統手藝傳承下去?","createTime":"2017-04-05T16:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T06:43:36.000Z","uid":89873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71914b1bc7909d252a9cc6e474ddf7324e8e797e","tid":188440,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"今日喺FB睇到100毛<br />\n拍咗段介紹關於磨刀師傅嘅片<br />\n之前都有好多唔同傳統手藝就黎失傳嘅報導<br />\n睇完果一刻真係有啲衝動想去拜師<br />\n<br />\n不過自己平時又要返工 <br />\n未計OT放工同放假都攰到唔想郁<br />\n而且咁多樣傳統手藝一個人去學唔係辦法<br />\n我就諗如果將呢啲傳統手藝搞啲興趣班<br />\n等而家嘅學生/有興趣嘅人放學放假去學<br />\n有冇得諗??? <br />\n各位Ching不妨講吓大家高見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外如果要搞 <br />\n我一個人未必有時間搞得成<br />\n真係成事的話<br />\n理想招集四至五個人<br />\n應該每人抽少少私人時間就搞掂 <br />\n有興趣可以Tg我<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/LiuWaiHung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLiuWaiHung&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f7e7ec97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/LiuWaiHung</a><br />\n<br />\n毒撚開Po 希望唔好無人理<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n100毛 磨刀師傅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tvmosthk/videos/1872462586335403/?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftvmosthk%2Fvideos%2F1872462586335403%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DPAGES_TIMELINE&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a168daec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tvmosthk/videos/1872462586335403/?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 臘腸師傅<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170115/19897124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170115%2F19897124&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=e246fd1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170115%2F19897124&h=fce66860\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170115/19897124</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 旗袍師傅<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160830/19754328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160830%2F19754328&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=7bb9a23d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160830%2F19754328&h=4f931d42\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160830/19754328</a><br />\n<br />\n東週刊 吹糖師傅<br />\n<a href=\"http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/56585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F56585&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0134c652\" target=\"_blank\">http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/56585</a>"},{"pid":"057252b34898fb2445ebf09442e0662216f6f1ca","tid":188440,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:20:29.000Z","msg":"自己俾個正皮自己先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d6b4d0f3615ae18e3b3c4cff921674dd7ac765","tid":188440,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"加人工"},{"pid":"cbe99b4ff02df01d8bab386af916b2ee5b25c30e","tid":188440,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"毒"},{"pid":"8920c0335ca4bd844da9b3107ca3d9664a987dc1","tid":188440,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"撚"},{"pid":"4edb8ec36c1d679ccf693b0478955f6344ab22de","tid":188440,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:21:49.000Z","msg":"開"},{"pid":"f4b869126020ee53c95f53b0bd2cc49ef4e74ed2","tid":188440,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"Po"},{"pid":"e0756e7005426bba0ce9598cb3ad3c3e8ae6de74","tid":188440,"uid":82540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20